I identified a reproducible gap: for U.S. Code citation-context lines that contain no modal cues and no recoverable section heading token, the parser currently returns zero formulas. I’m adding a final deterministic U.S.C. context fallback rule (frame IR) and then adding regression tests for the three packet citations through both regex and spaCy compiler paths.
